# RoadWatch — Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your API keys

# ── LLM Configuration (at least one recommended for AI chatbot) ──────────────
# Groq API — Free tier, fastest response (recommended)
# Get key: https://console.groq.com
GROQ_API_KEY=your_groq_api_key_here

# OpenAI API — Also enables vision-based road damage assessment
# Get key: https://platform.openai.com
OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_api_key_here

# Note: If neither key is set, the system uses a rule-based AI fallback
# which still demonstrates all features correctly.
